-- ALTER VIEW kpivis.dim_sales_force
-- AS
SELECT
    [SF_ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]
,[CICLO_TERRITORIO_DIVISAO]
,[BU]
,[DIVISAO]
,[TERRITORIO_CICLO]
,[CICLO_TERRITORIO]
,[MATRICULA_GD]
,[MATRICULA_GR]
,[TERR]
,[TERRITORIO_REP]
,[NOME_GRI/KAM]
,[NOME_GRI/KAM_COACH]
,[NOME_GN]
,[NOME_REP]
,[ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO]
,[TERRITORIO_NOME_REP]
,[TERRITORIO_GRI/KAM]
,[TERRITORIO_NOME_GRI/KAM]
,[TERRITORIO_GN]
,[TERRITORIO_NOME_GN]
,[STATUS]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/KPI Visitacao/dimensao_sales_force.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
[SF_ROW_ID_TERRITORIO]          VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CICLO_TERRITORIO_DIVISAO]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[BU]							VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DIVISAO]						VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_CICLO]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CICLO_TERRITORIO]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MATRICULA_GD]					VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MATRICULA_GR]					VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERR]							VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_REP]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME_GRI/KAM]					VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME_GRI/KAM_COACH]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME_GN]						VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[NOME_REP]						VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_NOME_REP]			VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_GRI/KAM]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_NOME_GRI/KAM]		VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_GN]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TERRITORIO_NOME_GN]			VARCHAR(150) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[STATUS]						VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) AS ROW
